<title>USA: Madison Sports names Ward as chairman.</title>
<headline>Madison Sports names Ward as chairman.</headline>
<dateline>CORONADO, Calif. 1996-10-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Madison Sports &amp; Entertainment Group Inc said Monday it has appointed Kevin Michael Ward as chairman and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Ward, previously co-chairman, replaces Joseph Radcliffe who has retired to pursue personal interests.</p>
<p>Ward will also serve as acting president until a suitable chief operating officer is recruited. Radcliffe will work with Ward as a consultant helping with a review of Madison's current operations, as well as pending acquisitions.</p>
